    <li><strong>Want one free tool for screenshots and videos across many platforms, no watermark, no signup?</strong> <a href="/editor">Easy Chat Maker</a>.</li>
    <li><strong>Need a ChatGPT, Claude or Gemini mockup?</strong> Easy Chat Maker — the other two don't do AI chats.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="ethics">Whichever you choose, use it responsibly</h2>
  <p>
    Every tool here makes convincing fakes, so the same rule applies to all of them: keep it <strong>clearly fictional</strong>. Fake chats for stories, memes, demos and teaching are fine; impersonating real people, fabricating evidence or misleading anyone is not. When in doubt, label it as a mockup.
  </p>

